<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-44-0941 </DOCNO><TEXT>Proposes a method of determining parameters of pressures appearing duringextraction of thick, steep coal seams, using horizontal-cut underhandmethod with hardening stowing, developed from the analysis of laboratoryand in-situ investigations carried out in the Prokop'evsk-Kiselevsk areaof the Kuzbass, and location in the seam of first horizontal slice, thicknessof sublevel posts left, sequence of slicing and physical-mechanical propertiesof the hardening stowing mass. Results obtained make it possible to determinethe safe and effective extraction of coal for specific mine conditions.3 refs.</TEXT></DOC>